{"tid":432650,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過訓教半夢半醒自己除左條底褲？","createTime":"2017-10-11T16:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T17:41:03.000Z","uid":61991,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3470bc28f459df4103f12663f1944bd24d7278ce","tid":432650,"uid":61991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"其實試過好多次，不過岩岩醒起試黎問下有冇巴打都係咁。<br />\n半夜醒左發覺條褲(連同底褲)除到去大腿，而條撚係扯緊。<br />\n諗返起其實岩岩半夢半醒之中迷迷糊糊除撚左條褲，依稀記得係夢入面係諗緊淫野。<br />\n<br />\n係咪得我先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴打試過？或者係夢入面做左其他野，醒左先發覺？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有試過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從來冇相關經歷"},{"pid":"ad86a1d882cf3c68b8e0b9830fb211bd7773378b","tid":432650,"uid":151833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"呢個情況應該發生起鍾意裸睡既朋友身上  著杉褲好難入睡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：裸睡6年左右  如果著左半夜會起身除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71eddc39dcf3a98135c2ef7792dbfb29e61259d","tid":432650,"uid":61991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個情況應該發生起鍾意裸睡既朋友身上  著杉褲好難入睡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：裸睡6年左右  如果著左半夜會起身除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我未試過裸睡<br />\n仲要唔係起身除褲，係睡夢中除"},{"pid":"defa828ff66e2a6a8394f041d4ea2f7c8d763506","tid":432650,"uid":123812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"有無諗過唔係你自己除？"},{"pid":"3a0198a571c693b3182271772aedfb221464a060","tid":432650,"uid":78322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會係伯母除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49896fab53d7cf9ad4d0041fda681675c9474e4","tid":432650,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"樓主好淫賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}